            android:text="Symptly Aware was created for the purpose of reporting statistics regarding symptoms for healthcare professionals. The app DOES NOT diagnose illnesses and SHOULD NOT replace the advice of a healthcare professional. If you are experiencing any of the appâ€™s listed symptoms, seek immediate medical attention."
